                "target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two groups of detectors were used:"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " plastic scintillation detector; dE strip",
                "Si-detector; dE0 start Si-detector. This group",
                "ensured transport of the beam particles into the",
                "target, their identification, and selection according",
                "to their trajectories."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 12 CsI(Tl) scintillation detectors with",
                "photomultipliers formed a segmented covering solid",
                "angle 0.9*4pi around the target."
              ]
            }
          ],
